"     Plotnick, LP, Klingensmith, GJ, Silverstein, J, Rosenbloom, AL. Diabetes Mellitus. In: Principles and Practice of Pediatric Endocrinology, Kappy, MS, Allen, DB, Geffner, ME (Eds), Charles C Thomas, Springfield, 2005. p. 635.",
"    </li>",
