"      Klingensmith G, Kaufman F, Schatz D, et al. Diabetes care in the school and day care setting. Diabetes Care 2004; 27 Suppl 1:S122.",
"     </a>",
"    </li>",
"    <li>",
"     <a class=\"nounderline abstract\" href=\"UTD.htm?1/7/1142/abstract/4\">",
"      Wagner J, Heapy A, James A, Abbott G. Brief report: glycemic control, quality of life, and school experiences among students with diabetes. J Pediatr Psychol 2006; 31:764.",
"     </a>",
"    </li>",
